OL,3,CSource of 'fly infestation' in
OL,4,CLlanelli confirmed
OL,6,FA metal recycling plant has been
OL,7,Fconfirmed as the source of a 'fly
OL,8,Finfestation' in Llanelli and ordered
OL,9,Fto take immediate action.
OL,11,FAMG Resources Limited, based in the
OL,12,FGlanymor area, has been issues with a
OL,13,F21 day enforcement notice by Natural
OL,14,FResources Wales (NRW).
OL,16,FThe recycling plant will now have to
OL,17,Ftake action on the management of waste
OL,18,Fon their site and "bring operations
OL,19,Fback into compliance with the
OL,20,Fconditions of its permit", NRW has
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
