OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784900896
OL,3,CSource of 'fly infestation' in
OL,4,CLlanelli confirmed
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales recently reported on
OL,7,Fthe infestation of flies in Llanelli
OL,8,Fwith many shops in the surrounding
OL,9,Fareas running out of fly spray.
OL,11,FResidents shared how bad the situation
OL,12,Fwas with one saying: ''They're just
OL,13,Feverywhere, everywhere you look...it's
OL,14,Fgotten worse and worse.''
OL,16,FSince issuing the statement, NRW said:
OL,17,F''We recognise the significant impact
OL,18,Fthis issue is having on residents and
OL,19,Fthe wider community.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
