PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784900896
OL,3,CSource of 'fly infestation' in
OL,4,CLlanelli confirmed
OL,6,F''The situation is being closely
OL,7,Fmonitored, and we will continue to
OL,8,Fdrive efforts to secure a swift and
OL,9,Flasting resolution for local
OL,10,Fresidents.''
OL,12,FIn a previous statement released on
OL,13,FThursday (23 July), Carmarthenshire
OL,14,FCountry Council said: ''The County
OL,15,FCouncil's Public Health Team has
OL,16,Finvested significant resources to help
OL,17,Ftackle the issue.''
